review_blob: Its the Ford truck of beer.. not flashy or particularly interesting, but gets the job done at an affordable price
Incredible abv at 20%, but not overpowering, still manages to maintain flavor of its weaker brethren the 60 and 90 minute ipas.
This is an Ohio favorite, so good they cant keep it on the shelf. Dark hoppy, yet sweet
